<template>
  {{msg}}
  {{ranNum}}
  <button @click="clickHandle">开始</button>
</template>

<script>
export default {
    name:'GetRandomNum',
    data(){
        return{
            msg:"开始抽奖",
            ranNum:" "
        }
    },
    methods:{
        clickHandle(){
            this.ranNum = Math.floor(Math.random()*10)
        }
        
    }


}
</script>
